Class Selector

java.lang.Object
  js.Disposable
      jsx.dom.query.Selector
Direct Known Subclasses:
Selector.And, Selector.Any, Selector.Even, Selector.Not, Selector.Nth, Selector.Odd, Selector.Or, Selector.Tag
public abstract class Selector
extends Disposable

An abstract base class that defines selectors to select nodes when paths perform queries.

Author:
J.J.Liu (Jianjun Liu) at http://www.jscripter.org

Method Detail

reset

public Selector reset()

Resets the selector and returns the new one.

This method simply returns the current selector without doing anything else. Overriding methods can do more as needed.

Returns:
The new selector reset from the current one.
Since:
1.0
